Description :
The "Pairs v1.0", application was developed as an example to first year Under Graduates on the module “Programming for Computing” at Sheffield Hallam University.
The application shows the usage of the following components, PictureBox/es, TextBox and Timer. In addition, it introduces secondary Windows and covers Arrays, Scope e.g., Local and Global variables.
The application was created by Kaytlen Tommis-birkett.
